03:44.648 --> 03:48.174
There's the outlaw.

03:48.194 --> 03:54.866
Lobo, wild wolf, go you silently.

03:56.368 --> 04:03.000
Off to the foothills in the shadow of each tree.

04:04.111 --> 04:11.180
You know there's danger, the danger I can't see.

04:12.141 --> 04:16.527
But you're not the outlaw, lobo.

04:16.867 --> 04:19.651
